name: Clover® Malawi Sable Farms Starbucks Reserve®
description:
Citrus, Cedar & Ginger
Sable Farm has a global reputation for producing top-quality coffee with environmentally-thoughtful practices. It’s also a pioneer in using solar coffee dryers!

name: Clover® Starbucks Reserve® Vietnam Da Lat
description:
Cocoa Peel and Toffee Nut
Anchored by the city of Da Lat, Vietnam’s Lam Dong Province provides a dreamlike setting for coffee cultivation—mist-shrouded pine forests, cool temperatures and volcanic soil. Farmers load just-picked coffee cherries onto small motorbikes and travel over rugged terrain to deliver high-quality crops. Their dedication culminates in this—a coffee every bit as distinctive as the land from which it came.
